{"tid":208270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家入嚟評下理.....","createTime":"2017-04-19T12:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T15:57:54.000Z","uid":73880,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e70c51d83d0d56961f191a756886afa15983a656","tid":208270,"uid":73880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"有個女人買咗一對全新嘅drkong鞋俾我仲有單有據咁影出嚟證明係該牌子嘅,咁交收嗰日我望左對鞋一眼就俾咗錢，去到今日我着咗落街唔夠5分鐘 對鞋一路蝕一路爛 我即刻上返樓睇一睇個鞋底，個鞋底蝕左5分一不特止仲要裂開咗，返到嚟我勁好語氣咁同個女人講對鞋着咗唔夠5分鐘就爛 ，可唔可以退錢或換貨..<br />\n佢就話喺網上買二手物品係有風險，我就話但係你話全新㗎喎，咁點解計二手，之後佢又話確實係全新佢無着過，咁我即刻攞起張單睇下原來係八年前買嘅...（即使你係無着過但係你放左係到八點，對鞋經過長年累月點都風化啦），仲點可以係計全新..<br />\n之後佢又話張單只不過用嚟證明係drkong，唔係對鞋嘅....而我後尾先發現佢影張單嗰陣特登遮住左日期，到我依加拎上手check返先知係零九年買嘅<br />\n咁我又話唔理點都好咁你件貨有問題係咪應該換先，佢又話我無理取鬧，話我着過對鞋冇人會幫着過嘅鞋退錢，我就話咁你出嚟買鞋對鞋有問題正常都可以退錢架 ，況且我只係着咗5分鐘就爛絕對唔係無理取鬧。<br />\n總之無論點佢都唔肯換，依家唔係錢嘅問題，係誠信嘅問題，一個人點解可以咁無賴，我真係只可以口同鼻拗....<br />\n以下係我同佢啲對話<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDe06bz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDe06bz.jpg&h=453049cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6q6AFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6q6AFz.jpg&h=b0c44722&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45oXw9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45oXw9C.jpg&h=543cc335&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DW4VVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DW4VVp.jpg&h=d7113e59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Sh7Q13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Sh7Q13.jpg&h=32a09cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/201033_84b1e2c2ce7637211932c6c8c5615193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F201033_84b1e2c2ce7637211932c6c8c5615193.jpg&h=2b8d416f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/201033_e288a07c7f4530c65becbbefd34672a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F201033_e288a07c7f4530c65becbbefd34672a5.jpg&h=e2b399d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/201034_5bdadac999b8135fe6e0d44b8fce88e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F201034_5bdadac999b8135fe6e0d44b8fce88e6.jpg&h=9eb73712&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rrdJ3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rrdJ3b.jpg&h=ae00f08a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38ed237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38ed237.jpg&h=7b3de121&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/201105_7e309597b296d325963a21c2f8ef24d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F201105_7e309597b296d325963a21c2f8ef24d0.jpg&h=5b71cfd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eaf2220ba53ddaf1fb1f0070d692715f541b01f","tid":208270,"uid":73880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"講到一嚿嚿咁希望有人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  總之好明顯係個女人特登買對九年前買落嘅鞋比我又唔認，仲要講埋一大堆歪理...我淨係想放上嚟俾大家評下理，如果最後真係發現係佢錯我決定要放佢電話同埋個交易網ac俾大家小心呢啲奸商"},{"pid":"f9265c88f2bfe3f29750e89d87eb3fe04098b5c3","tid":208270,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，咁點解一開始你要起網上買"},{"pid":"0396ae3861290419207932602591c970eb044ce6","tid":208270,"uid":5402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"你自己check左無問題先買<br />\n理得佢放左9 年定90 年？"},{"pid":"e5fd8087c036dbd6b3639a7539b352196afd4523","tid":208270,"uid":56313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"自己唔check清楚係度怪人